name: Primordia Saturnus 03
description:
Primordia Saturnus is the first species of Mildewds available on any blockchain. Each Dewd in this "flush" (mushrooms grow in flushes) of characters is a one-of-a-kind artwork created by our fifth generation Primordia Saturnus art machine.

Mildewds is an exploration of the potential and limits of modern digital art tools to generate characters with personality and scenes with narrative. We chose mushrooms because of the mystery, variety and potential they represent to us.

To learn more about the Mildewds project visit [https://www.voidstrummer.com/mildewds](https://www.voidstrummer.com/mildewds).
